{"tid":532173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北市清潔隊員錄取476名　學歷以大學畢業者居多","createTime":"2018-01-17T14:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T07:02:43.000Z","uid":84436,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fa3d4afcff20150b80832201df12a7b9c2a0cf66","tid":532173,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:27:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180116/1278859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180116%2F1278859%2F&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=26b85500\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180116%2F1278859%2F&h=ddcb5d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180116/1278859/</a><br />\n<br />\n北市環保局最近公布106年儲備清潔隊員甄試結果，在3560位考生應試中，經過體能測驗及筆試測驗，最後錄取476人，其中一般類組330人、保障類組146人，錄取率約13.4%。北市環保局表示，此次錄取者最高齡為61歲、最年輕為16歲，而多數錄取者為20至29歲及30至39歲之青壯年均佔38.24%，至於學歷則以大學畢業者最多，佔40.55%，其次為高職畢業者，佔16.18%。<br />\n <br />\n環保局說，本次錄取人員由3560人中脫穎而出，不僅具備優異的體能狀況，在環保常識筆試成績亦接近滿分，是台北市新一批環保生力軍。錄取的儲備人員將以一般類組與保障類組7：3交叉方式排定進用順序，並依序通知到工，另經該局估算，第1批清潔隊員職缺預計70餘名，將於2月辦理公開分發作業後開始上工。（林媛玲／台北報導）"},{"pid":"baba69964acc8c0d079efaf4fc644beaf6f5c207","tid":532173,"uid":43042,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"台灣大學=公廁"},{"pid":"bfcc42179abe259a24c3a3e64dc1e4bbb821f101","tid":532173,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"台灣10個有9個都大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef7e49023381006c8f8d617799185441a5737d0","tid":532173,"uid":26071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180116/1278859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180116%2F1278859%2F&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=26b85500\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180116%2F1278859%2F&h=ddcb5d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180116/1278859/</a><br />\n<br />\n北市環保局最近公布106年儲備清潔隊員甄試結果，在3560位考生應試中，經過體能測驗及筆試測驗，最後錄取476人，其中一般類組330人、保障類組146人，<span style=\"color: red;\">錄取率約13.4%</span>。北市環保局表示，此次錄取者最高齡為61歲、最年輕為16歲，而多數錄取者為20至29歲及30至39歲之青壯年均佔38.24%，至於學歷則以大學畢業者最多，佔40.55%，其次為高職畢業者，佔16.18%。<br />\n <br />\n環保局說，本次錄取人員由3560人中脫穎而出，不僅具備優異的體能狀況，<span style=\"color: red;\">在環保常識筆試成績亦接近滿分</span>，是台北市新一批環保生力軍。錄取的儲備人員將以一般類組與保障類組7：3交叉方式排定進用順序，並依序通知到工，另經該局估算，第1批清潔隊員職缺預計70餘名，將於2月辦理公開分發作業後開始上工。（林媛玲／台北報導）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n掃地都考唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9fcc13915036f32058c0eadefcf3da3e6ec2b6","tid":532173,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"佢咁講法好似難過考紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62db996af60d7ce5d064b08f75e908c4b0c2149a","tid":532173,"uid":164920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"台灣個鳩個都大學生架啦"},{"pid":"e28951a93958e474630b80795d2a8127fd91fbfb","tid":532173,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"屌清潔阿姐"},{"pid":"18ef02107ba4f43b0c9868195421e13ef84606eb","tid":532173,"uid":25866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e28951a93958e474630b80795d2a8127fd91fbfb","tid":532173,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"屌清潔阿姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"人地好